   <conbody>
      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The PEW solutions needed a larger number of secondary devices
than the SDC. To connect all devices three gateways had to be used,
so the solutions contains three setups, one for each LUFP7 gateway
(A060, A062 and A064).</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The first PEW gateway setup (A060) contains
one IM400 insulated monitoring device and three IFL12MC insulation
fault locators.</p>
         <fig class="- topic/fig ">
            <title class="- topic/title ">PEW Distribution A/B Setup — LUFP7 (A060)</title>
            <image href="../Images/Cablink_Overview_PEW-001_0000412332.svg"
                   placement="inline"
                   class="- topic/image "/>
         </fig>
      </div>
      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The second and third PEW gateway setups (A062, A064) are identical
and only contains three IFL12MC insulation fault locators (no IM400).</p>
